results.name: Triangle read by rows: T(m,n) = number of partitions of the multiset with m elements and signature corresponding to n-th integer partition (A194602).
comment: This triangle shows the same numbers in each row as A129306 and A096443, but in this arrangement the multisets in column n correspond to the n-th integer partition in the infinite order defined by A194602.
Row lengths: A000041 (partition numbers), Row sums: A035310
Last in row: end-1: A091437, end: A000041 (partition numbers)
The rightmost columns form a reflected version of the triangle A126442:
A249619 shows the number of permutations of the same multisets.
